quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,137,"Ibi (twemera) si ibindi, usibye ko ari imigenzo n’imyemerere (gakondo) y’abo hambere"
  26,138,Kandi ntituzahanwa (nk’uko ubivuga)
  26,139,"Nuko baramuhinyura, maze turabarimbura. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ikimenyetso (kigaragaza ubushobozi bwa Allah), ariko abenshi muri bo ntibemera"
  26,140,"Kandi mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wawe ni We Munyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirimbabazi"
  26,141,Abantu bo mu bwoko bwa Thamudu (na bo) bahinyuye intumwa
  26,142,Ubwo umuvandimwe wabo Swalehe yababwiraga ati “Ese ntimwatinya Allah?”
  26,143,“Mu by’ukuri njye ndi intumwa yanyu yizewe.”
  26,144,“Bityo nimugandukire Allah kandi munyumvire.”
  26,145,"“Kandi ntabwo (kubagezaho ubutumwa) mbibasabira igihembo, kuko ibihembo byanjye biri kwa Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose.”"
  26,146,"“Ese (mukeka ko) muzarekerwa mu byo murimo aha (ku isi, ngo mubeho) mutekanye (nta bihano nta no gupfa)?”"
  26,147,"“Mu mirima (myiza) ndetse n’imigezi (itemba),”"
  26,148,“No mu bihingwa (bitandukanye) n’imitende ifite imigondoro yoroshye?”
  26,149,“Kandi muhanga amazu mu misozi mu buryo bwa gihanga.”
  26,150,“Bityo nimugandukire Allah kandi munyumvire.”
  26,151,“Kandi ntimukumvire amategeko y’inkozi z’ibibi.”
  26,152,“Ba bandi bakora ubwononnyi ku isi kandi ntibagire ibyo batunganya.”
  26,153,Baravuga bati “Mu by’ukuri wowe (Swalehe) uri umwe mu bantu barozwe!”
  26,154,“Wowe nta kindi uri cyo usibye ko uri umuntu nkatwe. Ngaho zana ikimenyetso (kigaragaza ko uri intumwa) niba koko uri mu banyakuri!”
  26,155,"(Swalehe) aravuga ati “Dore iyi ngamiya y’ishashi, izajya inywa amazi umunsi umwe namwe munywe ku wundi munsi uzwi.”"
  26,156,“Kandi muramenye ntimuzayigirire nabi mutazavaho mukagerwaho n’ibihano by’umunsi uhambaye.”
  26,157,Ariko barayishe maze basigara bicuza
  26,158,"Nuko bagerwaho n’ibihano. Mu by’ukuri muri ibyo harimo ikimenyetso (kigaragaza ubushobozi bwa Allah), ariko abenshi muri bo ntibemera"
  26,159,"Kandi mu by’ukuri Nyagasani wawe ni We Munyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirimpuhwe"